And then what you gonna do?
Tell the police?

709
01:00:38,599 --> 01:00:42,051
- 你在搞笑嗎？
- 我之前有提到過警察嗎？
- You want me to laugh?
- Who said anything about the police?

710
01:00:42,228 --> 01:00:44,386
我會把這些信息與你的競爭對手分享
I'm gonna share the information
with the competition,

711
01:00:44,564 --> 01:00:46,224
我還沒干掉的那些家伙
the ones I haven't already killed.

712
01:00:46,399 --> 01:00:48,854
我會拿光你所有的東西
Anything they don't take from you,
I will.

713
01:00:49,026 --> 01:00:52,312
首先我會帶走你漂亮的老婆
First I'm gonna take your trophy wife.

714
01:00:52,488 --> 01:00:55,442
然後是你的孩子們
Then I'm gonna take
your trophy children.

715
01:00:55,616 --> 01:00:57,159
我會讓你一無所有
I'm gonna leave you with nothing.

716
01:00:57,285 --> 01:00:59,776
當我完事後，你就什麼都不是了
When I'm done, you won't even be
a memory of a memory.

717
01:01:00,997 --> 01:01:04,366
- 不過這些都沒必要發生
- 你想要什麼？
- But that doesn't have to happen.
- What do you want?

718
01:01:05,334 --> 01:01:07,576
- 我想知道保險箱裡有什麼
- 什麼保險箱？
- I wanna know what's in the safe.
- What safe?

719
01:01:07,754 --> 01:01:10,873
那個女孩給我密碼的那個保險箱
The safe the girl gave me
the combination to. That safe.

720
01:01:13,176 --> 01:01:15,168
三千萬美元
$30 million.

721
01:01:16,846 --> 01:01:19,717
那孩子本來要去拿第二個密碼，第二個保險箱裡有什麼？
Kid was on her way to get a second
number. What's in the second safe?

722
01:01:20,767 --> 01:01:24,385
值三千萬美元的東西
Something won'th $30 million.

723
01:01:24,562 --> 01:01:26,887
- 給誰？
- 不知道
- To who?
- No idea.

724
01:01:28,274 --> 01:01:30,730
那是因為你只有小聰明，埃米爾
That's 'cause
you're only half-smart, Emile.

725
01:01:32,904 --> 01:01:34,647
那麼，我們這麼說定了…
So here's the deal.

726
01:01:34,822 --> 01:01:37,527
你告訴我第一個保險箱在哪，我拿了錢就放你兒子
You tell me where the first safe is,
I take the money and let your boy go.

727
01:01:37,700 --> 01:01:40,452
騙我的話你就死定了，說到做到
Lie to me and yourworld ends.
You have my word on that.

728
01:01:40,620 --> 01:01:44,664
白癡！我知道一個人是否獨行
Idiot. I know
when a man is working alone

729
01:01:44,832 --> 01:01:47,288
而你正好只身一人
and you're as alone as one can be.

730
01:01:47,460 --> 01:01:50,377
你需要一支隊伍才能靠近保險箱
You need a small army
to get near that safe,

731
01:01:50,546 --> 01:01:52,705
我有這種隊伍
the kind of army I have.

732
01:01:52,882 --> 01:01:56,832
曾經有過！我時間不多
Had. It's been shrinking by the minute.

733
01:01:58,096 --> 01:02:00,883
最後一次機會，否則我就掛電話修理你兒子了
Last chance before I hang up
and go to work on your son.

734
01:02:05,520 --> 01:02:07,512
你要殺我嗎，收垃圾的？
Going to kill me, garbage man?

735
01:02:09,107 --> 01:02:12,392
你那天就可以把我們都干掉的，是嗎？
You could have taken us out that day,
couldn't you?

736
01:02:12,568 --> 01:02:14,691
但是你只是跪在那裡
But you just sat there,

737
01:02:14,862 --> 01:02:17,567
讓我們毀掉你，讓你變得一無是處
let us ruin you,
let us make you nothing.

738
01:02:17,740 --> 01:02:21,868
我猜是保險箱給了你新的動力，是嗎，收垃圾的？
I guess finding out about that safe gave
you new motivation, eh garbage man?

739
01:02:23,079 --> 01:02:25,486
如果我是你就不會浪費口舌
I wouldn't spend my time talking
if I were you.

740
01:02:26,249 --> 01:02:30,578
會祈禱事情結束時，那小女孩還活著
Spend it praying that when this is over
that little girl's still alive.

741
01:02:34,424 --> 01:02:36,416
祈禱！
Pray.

742
01:02:44,684 --> 01:02:45,680
時間地點？
When and where?

743
01:02:45,852 --> 01:02:48,936
橋下的地下道，一小時後
The underpass under the bridge,
one hour.

744
01:02:52,734 --> 01:02:56,648
對不起，那些俄國人出現時我用槍指著你
I'm sorry I pointed a gun at you
when the Russians attacked us, Mei.

745
01:02:58,072 --> 01:03:00,029
- 那只是…
- 生意而已…我知道的
- It was...
- Business. I know.

746
01:03:00,199 --> 01:03:02,607
很好，很好，你理解
It's good. It's good you understand.

747
01:03:02,785 --> 01:03:04,861
我們會搞定這一切
We're going to get this done

748
01:03:05,037 --> 01:03:07,279
然後你跟我和韓叔一起就安全了
and you'll be safe
with me and Uncle Han.

749
01:03:09,083 --> 01:03:10,625
我保證做一個好父親
I promise to be a better father to you

750
01:03:10,793 --> 01:03:12,952
比那個拋棄你和你母親的家伙更好
than the one
who left you and your mother.

751
01:03:16,716 --> 01:03:19,385
這個世界上沒人比我更關心你
There's no one in the world
who cares more about you.

752
01:03:20,720 --> 01:03:22,926
你知道的，是嗎？
You know that, don't you?

753
01:03:52,335 --> 01:03:54,624
人都到了
Well, the gang's all here.

754
01:03:54,796 --> 01:03:56,587
差不多
Almost.

755
01:03:56,756 --> 01:04:00,006
- 伯尼生病了？
- 他在醫院，混蛋！
- Reddick have to call in sick?
- He's in the hospital, dickhead.

756
01:04:00,176 --> 01:04:03,877
- 你打壞了他的氣管
- 我從來不知道氣管還能被打壞
- You broke his trachea.
- I didn't know a trachea could break.

757
01:04:04,055 --> 01:04:06,012
- 希望他們能修好
- 是嗎！不如讓我先修理你？
- Hope they can fix it.
- Yeah? How about I fix you?

758
01:04:06,182 --> 01:04:08,755
嘿！嘿！嘿！嘿！別這樣！
Hey, hey, hey, hey. Not here.

759
01:04:09,894 --> 01:04:13,429
好久不見，路克，不過我並不想念你
It's been a while, Luke.
Can't say I missed you.

760
01:04:14,941 --> 01:04:18,773
- 那麼，有話直說吧
- 帶了我要的東西沒？
- So, let's get down to business.
- Did you bring what I asked for?

761
01:04:23,199 --> 01:04:25,441
- 托斯卡尼的
- 還有呢？
- Toscanni's.
- Where else?

762
01:04:42,385 --> 01:04:44,792
味道不錯！
Mmm. That's good.

763
01:04:59,235 --> 01:05:01,228
我整晚都在餐館裡
Been in restaurants all night.

764
01:05:02,321 --> 01:05:04,314
