All I got served was lead.

765
01:05:10,621 --> 01:05:13,575
- 有火嗎？
- 去你的！
- Anyone got a light?
- You know what? Screw this.

766
01:05:13,750 --> 01:05:16,205
聽著，隊長，你讓我們過來，我們過來了
Look, Captain, you asked us
to come here, so we came.

767
01:05:16,419 --> 01:05:19,040
但我不會站在這裡聽這混蛋胡扯
But I ain't gonna sit here
and listen to this scumbag's big mouth.

768
01:05:19,213 --> 01:05:21,206
閉嘴，科夫克斯！
Shut up, Kolfax.

769
01:05:21,799 --> 01:05:24,337
還沒戒煙，哈？
Still haven't quit, huh?

770
01:05:34,812 --> 01:05:37,434
嘿，嘿，這是什麼？
Hey. Hey, what the hell is that?

771
01:05:37,607 --> 01:05:39,599
裝有三千萬美元保險箱的密碼
Combination of the safe
with 30 million bucks in it.

772
01:05:39,776 --> 01:05:42,267
- 哇，哇！你在干嘛？
- 你個狗屎
- Whoa, whoa, whoa.
- Filthy piece of shit.

773
01:05:42,445 --> 01:05:45,362
現在這密碼存在我腦子裡了
The only place it exists now is in here.

774
01:05:45,531 --> 01:05:48,069
當你們手癢想扣扳機時，記住這點
Remember that next time
your little triggerfinger gets itchy.

775
01:05:48,242 --> 01:05:49,487
為什麼韓礁會把它藏在
Why would Han Jiou stash it

776
01:05:49,660 --> 01:05:52,234
