Because of sleaze-bucket cops
like you, Benoit,

778
01:05:54,791 --> 01:05:57,329
去賭窩收保護費腐敗警察
who collect off of Chinatowrs
busiest gambling den.

779
01:05:57,502 --> 01:05:59,909
想不吸引警察的注意
