without attracting police attention?

781
01:06:01,839 --> 01:06:05,291
隊長,我們怎麼知道這混蛋不是在玩我們？他是個流浪漢！
Captain, why do we know this son of
a bitch on the level, huh? He's a bum.

782
01:06:05,468 --> 01:06:07,461
你從哪得到的消息？
Where'd you get your information?

783
01:06:08,387 --> 01:06:10,464
今晚會有個交易
There's an exchange happening tonight.

784
01:06:10,598 --> 01:06:12,756
三合會半數交易額都在賭場保險箱裡
The Triad half of the deal
is in a safe in the casino.

785
01:06:12,934 --> 01:06:16,599
我一人搞不定，所以我叫了你們，老朋友們
No way I could get to it on my own,
so I called on you, my old pals.

786
01:06:17,980 --> 01:06:20,471
三千萬美元分六份依然是很大一筆錢
30 million split six ways
is still a lot of money.

787
01:06:23,277 --> 01:06:27,192
我們風險太大，隊長，尤其是你
We're risking a lot, Captain.
You especially.

788
01:06:27,365 --> 01:06:29,938
所有人都知道你前途光明
Everybody knows you got a bright future.

789
01:06:30,118 --> 01:06:33,072
