Promised by who? His Honour?

790
01:06:33,246 --> 01:06:35,950
他跟你承諾什麼了，沃夫？
What carrot
is he teasing you with, Wolf?

791
01:06:36,124 --> 01:06:38,496
若他知道你所掌握的，他還會放過你？
He's gonna let you out in the street
knowing what you know now?

792
01:06:38,668 --> 01:06:39,830
你什麼意思？
What's that supposed to mean?

793
01:06:40,002 --> 01:06:42,873
意思是，他的第二任期快到頭了，什麼保證都是屁
His second term is gonna come to an end
and his hold on the city goes poof.

794
01:06:43,047 --> 01:06:45,503
就跟普通公民一樣
Just like that he's Joe Citizen again.

795
01:06:45,633 --> 01:06:47,922
三千萬是一筆不錯的退休金
30 million would be
a nice retirement package.

796
01:06:48,094 --> 01:06:49,339
他給中國佬什麼好處？
What's he giving the Chinks?

797
01:06:49,512 --> 01:06:53,379
如果我知道，還會跟你們這幫混蛋站在這裡？
If I knew that, I wouldn't be standing
here with you assholes, would I?

798
01:06:55,101 --> 01:06:56,678
光明未來，哈？
A bright future, huh?

799
01:06:56,853 --> 01:06:58,561
頭條
Big headlines.

800
01:06:58,730 --> 01:07:02,181
“英雄警察破獲紐約最大的地下賭博巢穴”
"Hero cops take down New York City's
biggest underground gambling operation."

801
01:07:02,358 --> 01:07:05,359
每人五百萬美元，且沒人知道
Five million bucks apiece
that no one will ever know about,

802
01:07:05,528 --> 01:07:07,817
就當是額外甜頭
just to give it that extra sweet taste.

803
01:07:25,673 --> 01:07:29,623
好了，誰進去過？拜托，誰進去過？
All right, who's been in there?
For Christ's sake, who's been in there?

804
01:07:29,802 --> 01:07:32,127
- 我，隊長
- 你倆做先鋒
- Me, Cap.
- You two, you're on point.

805
01:07:32,305 --> 01:07:35,092
裡面都是平民，看准了打
Place is packed with civilians,
so exercise some judgement.

806
01:07:35,266 --> 01:07:37,389
記住只有我有密碼
Remember, I got the combination.

807
01:07:37,560 --> 01:07:39,802
如果你們想要錢，掩護好我
You want that money, watch my back.

808
01:07:57,163 --> 01:07:59,239
你要去哪？
Where are you going?

809
01:07:59,415 --> 01:08:02,202
別動！待著！
Don't move! Stay!

810
01:08:16,099 --> 01:08:17,474
讓開！走！
Out of the way! Move!

811
01:08:35,159 --> 01:08:36,618
嘿，你，去死吧！
Hey, you, settle down!

812
01:08:48,881 --> 01:08:50,079
這裡！走！
This way. Let's go.

813
01:09:34,719 --> 01:09:35,999
小心
Heads up.

814
01:09:44,395 --> 01:09:46,518
走
Go.

815
01:09:57,575 --> 01:09:59,698
科夫克斯，干掉他
Kolfax, take him out.

816
01:10:06,209 --> 01:10:07,917
掩護他
Cover him.

817
01:10:50,420 --> 01:10:52,246
打開它，開槍！
Open it. Take it!

