- Captain Wolf, you need an ambulance.
- I need a fleet of ambulances.

847
01:14:39,023 --> 01:14:41,894
趕緊叫救護車，懂嗎？我自己開去醫院
Call it in, will you? I'll take
my own busted ass to the hospital.

848
01:14:45,029 --> 01:14:46,523
演技不錯
Not bad.

849
01:14:46,697 --> 01:14:49,485
如果你不是個兩面派，我幾乎都喜歡上你了
If you werert such a double-dealing
asshole, I could almost like you.

850
01:14:49,659 --> 01:14:52,114
是幾乎！開車！
Almost. Drive.

851
01:14:57,291 --> 01:14:58,916
只是劃傷
It's a scratch.

852
01:15:02,213 --> 01:15:05,997
我不會殺你，但我可沒說讓你住大酒店
I'm not gonna kill you, but I didn't say
I was putting you up at the Ritz.

853
01:15:14,350 --> 01:15:15,844
沃夫
Wolf.

854
01:15:16,018 --> 01:15:18,011
我需要錢，丹尼
I have your money, Danny.

855
01:15:19,772 --> 01:15:20,768
什麼？
What?

856
01:15:22,483 --> 01:15:24,143
你聽見了
You heard me.

857
01:15:24,318 --> 01:15:27,687
三千萬！五千份一千美元的支票
30 million. Five-thousand
and one-thousand dollar bills.

858
01:15:27,864 --> 01:15:29,607
- 我想談談
- 不行
- I wanna talk.
- No.

859
01:15:29,782 --> 01:15:32,190
你需要的是冷靜下來我們好談點正常的
No, what you wanna do is calm down
so we can talk like adults.

860
01:15:32,368 --> 01:15:34,028
閉嘴，丹尼
Shut it, Danny.

861
01:15:34,162 --> 01:15:36,285
我是想談，不過不是和你談
I wanna talk,
but I don't wanna talk to you.

862
01:15:36,456 --> 01:15:37,914
我要和你男朋友談
I wanna talk to your boyfriend.

863
01:15:42,336 --> 01:15:44,044
我是亞歷克斯
This is Alex.

864
01:15:44,172 --> 01:15:46,627
好久不見，亞歷克斯
Been a while, Alex.

865
01:15:46,799 --> 01:15:49,207
- 你怎麼拿到這號碼的？
- 別這樣，亞歷克斯
- How'd you get this number?
- Come on, Alex.

866
01:15:49,385 --> 01:15:51,508
順著市長的味就能找到你
Reach up the mayor's ass, there you are.

867
01:15:53,723 --> 01:15:56,130
男人就該有男人樣，哈？
A mars gotta do
what a mars gotta do, huh?

868
01:15:56,309 --> 01:15:58,385
他總比安妮這誘餌好
He's a better catch
than Annie was anyway.

869
01:15:58,561 --> 01:16:01,895
我一直不解你為什麼會勾搭上那樣一頭奶牛
I never understood
how you hooked up with a cow like that.

870
01:16:02,065 --> 01:16:04,734
絕不是因為她的長相，而是她的幽默感
It was never about her looks.
It was her sense of humour.

871
01:16:04,901 --> 01:16:07,107
她現在沒那麼搞笑了，不是麼？
She's not so funny now, is she?

872
01:16:07,278 --> 01:16:09,769
不是了，我也一樣
No, she's not. Neither am I.

873
01:16:11,699 --> 01:16:14,486
我拿到了錢，亞歷克斯，我殺了很多人才弄到的
I have the money, Alex.
I had to kill a lot of people to get it.

874
01:16:14,660 --> 01:16:16,071
所以聽著
So listen up.

875
01:16:17,455 --> 01:16:20,705
你還沒交換過密碼，另一個保險箱裡是什麼？
You haven't made the combination
exchange yet. What's in the other safe?

876
01:16:20,875 --> 01:16:23,366
一張碟片
A disc.

877
01:16:23,544 --> 01:16:26,118
名字，錢的來龍去脈…
Names, money trails.

878
01:16:26,297 --> 01:16:29,298
當指揮官派我們幫丹尼清理城市時
When our commanders sent the two of us
to help Danny clean up the city,

879
01:16:29,467 --> 01:16:30,498
他們附加了一個條件
they attached a price.

880
01:16:30,676 --> 01:16:32,219
作為交換，丹尼要自尋財路
In exchange, Danny looked the other way

881
01:16:32,386 --> 01:16:35,340
而每筆被當做恐怖組織查抄的集團資金
while the assets seized from every group
deemed a terrorist organisation

882
01:16:35,515 --> 01:16:37,388
則裝進了他們的私人腰包
were funnelled
into their private accounts.

883
01:16:37,558 --> 01:16:39,136
驚訝是他們受驚需要保護時
Amazing what people
let you get away with

884
01:16:39,310 --> 01:16:41,219
卻把你趕走了
when they're scared
and wanna feel protected.

885
01:16:41,396 --> 01:16:43,222
驚訝的是有那麼多小人
Amazing how many scumbags
there are out there

886
01:16:43,398 --> 01:16:44,975
都等著乘機牟利
waiting to take advantage of it.

887
01:16:45,149 --> 01:16:46,774
- 難道你沒有麼？
- 我退出了
- Like you didn't?
- I quit.

888
01:16:46,943 --> 01:16:49,944
你以為這能幫那些被你私自送去見上帝的人
Bet that helps all those souls you sent
to meet their maker without due process

889
01:16:50,113 --> 01:16:51,275
省下很多功夫嗎？
rest a whole lot easier.

890
01:16:51,447 --> 01:16:53,404
你以為你在拳擊場上
You thought you could atone
by climbing into a cage

891
01:16:53,574 --> 01:16:55,650
被人隨意毆打就能贖罪嗎？
and allowing yourself
to get beaten to a pulp?

892
01:16:55,827 --> 01:16:57,570
別給我說教了，路克！
Don't fucking preach at me, Luke.

893
01:16:57,745 --> 01:17:00,497
我只是收錢辦事
I'm getting paid for services rendered.

894
01:17:00,665 --> 01:17:05,125
是啊，你把碟片賣給中國人好讓他們勒索我們上司
Right. You sell the disc to the Chinese
so they can blackmail our old honchos,

895
01:17:05,294 --> 01:17:08,995
然後拿著三千萬美元和丹尼去巴哈馬別墅逍遙自在
take the 30 mill and waltz off
with Danny to a villa in the Bahamas.

896
01:17:09,173 --> 01:17:11,711
是巴厘島，不過無所謂了，不是麼？
Bali, but whatever, right?

897
01:17:11,884 --> 01:17:14,921
那麼，就算你知道了，又如何？
So, now you know. Now what?

898
01:17:15,138 --> 01:17:16,929
現在你要應付我
Now you're dealing with me.

899
01:17:17,140 --> 01:17:19,678
- 好吧，我退出
- 不行
- All right, I'm turning around.
- No, you're not.

900
01:17:20,893 --> 01:17:23,515
你說什麼？你已經拿到錢了
What are you talking about?
You've got the money.

901
01:17:23,688 --> 01:17:27,982
- 中國人手裡沒有我要的了
- 不，他們有我想要的
- The Chinese have nothing I care about.
- No. They have something I do.

902
01:17:46,502 --> 01:17:50,167
把你保險箱密碼給這女孩，她會給你我們的
Give the girl the combination to your
safe and she will give you our number.

903
01:17:50,339 --> 01:17:52,166
我們到你的地方，你去我們的
We go to your location, you go to ours.

904
01:17:52,300 --> 01:17:55,633
當我們拿到碟片，我們會給你解密密碼
When we've gotten the disc,
we will explain the code

905
01:17:55,803 --> 01:17:57,001
你拿到你的錢
and you'll get the cash.

906
01:17:57,805 --> 01:17:59,798
一言為定
That's the deal.

907
01:18:00,558 --> 01:18:03,678
- 說說看吧
- 這是個很長的數字
- Let's hear it.
- It's a very long number.

908
01:18:03,853 --> 01:18:06,344
你最好能記下來
You'll want to write it down.

909
01:18:06,522 --> 01:18:08,479
感謝上帝我還帶了筆，哈？
Thank goodness I brought a pen, huh?

910
01:18:18,409 --> 01:18:20,069
你最好閉上眼睛
You might wanna close your eyes.

911
01:18:22,330 --> 01:18:23,789
隨你便吧
Have it your way.

912
01:18:36,219 --> 01:18:38,211
快接，路克
Come on, Luke.

913
01:18:40,431 --> 01:18:42,839
老地方，就你和我
The old place, just you and me.

914
01:18:45,686 --> 01:18:47,097
你是路克的朋友嗎？
You're a friend of Luke?

915
01:18:49,732 --> 01:18:51,808
這不是你該關心的
Not as far as you're concerned.

916
01:19:03,955 --> 01:19:06,113
今晚席卷整個紐約的暴力活動
The violence
that has rocked the city tonight

917
01:19:06,290 --> 01:19:07,666
依舊持續，不到一小時前
continued in a bloody gun battle

918
01:19:07,834 --> 01:19:10,788
中國城一家夜總會爆發了血腥槍戰
in a Chinatown nightclub
less than an hourago.

919
01:19:10,962 --> 01:19:13,250
- 這已經完全失控了
- 你以為呢？
- This is really getting out of hand.
- You think?

920
01:19:13,381 --> 01:19:15,420
謝謝提醒
Thanks for that insight.

921
01:19:15,591 --> 01:19:18,426
市長，亞歷克斯•羅瑟斯在你私人專線上
Your Honour,
Alex Rosers on your private line.

922
01:19:18,594 --> 01:19:20,089
他說有急事
He says that it's urgent.

923
01:19:20,263 --> 01:19:23,596
- 打擾一下，市長
- 我5分鍾後回來，現在別煩我
- Excuse me, Your Honour.
- Back in five. Don't bother me now.

924
01:19:23,766 --> 01:19:25,973
他為什麼不打我手機？
Why didn't he call me on my cellphone?

925
01:19:26,144 --> 01:19:29,061
我記得讓你把所有電話都接到我的…
I thought I told you to put
all my calls through to the...

926
01:19:30,022 --> 01:19:33,142
我一直跟你說這裡保安水平太差
I always told you this place
had lousy security standards.

927
01:19:35,403 --> 01:19:38,570
那是因為沒人會瘋到像你一樣來這殺人
Because nobody's been crazy enough to
come in here and pull a stunt like this.

928
01:19:38,740 --> 01:19:42,524
- 你有種，路克
- 是啊，真是驚訝我還能走路
- You got some balls, Luke.
- Yeah, amazing I can even walk.

929
01:19:42,702 --> 01:19:44,279
給我碟片
The disc.

930
01:19:44,412 --> 01:19:46,737
什麼？你以為我會傻到讓中國幫派
What, you think I'm stupid enough
to let a gang of Chinese

931
01:19:46,914 --> 01:19:49,322
穿過前門進到房間來拿它？
walk up the front steps and collect it
from me in my living room?

932
01:19:49,500 --> 01:19:53,165
- 它在離這很遠的保險箱裡
- 我不認為你很蠢
- It's in a safe far away from here.
- I don't think you're stupid.

933
01:19:53,337 --> 01:19:56,422
所以我不認為你只有一份拷貝
Which is why I don't for a second
believe you gave away the only copy.

934
01:19:56,591 --> 01:19:58,797
我會去見亞歷克斯
I'm going to meet Alex.

935
01:19:58,968 --> 01:20:02,419
你先給我碟片，不然我就在非要害的部位給你一槍
First you give me the disc or I'll put
bullets in places that won't kill you

936
01:20:02,597 --> 01:20:05,930
讓你下半輩子生不如死
but make you spend
the rest of your life wishing I had.

937
01:20:14,067 --> 01:20:15,644
滿意了?
Satisfied?

938
01:20:15,818 --> 01:20:18,190
我要確認一下這不是“金剛葫蘆娃”
I wanna make sure
it's not ABBA'sGreatest Hits.

939
01:20:28,164 --> 01:20:29,907
亞歷克斯會殺了你的,你知道的
Alex will kill you, you know.

940
01:20:31,209 --> 01:20:33,534
嗯，或許吧
Yeah, probably.

941
01:21:18,423 --> 01:21:21,708
上帝，路克，你氣色很不好
Jesus. Luke, you look like hell.

942
01:21:22,635 --> 01:21:27,297
酒精而已，缺少睡眠和陽光
Just alcohol, lack of sunlight,
sleep deprivation.

943
01:21:28,891 --> 01:21:30,884
除此以外，我感覺不錯
Other than that, I feel great.

944
01:21:32,979 --> 01:21:37,273
呵，我在想，我們在這裡拋過多少屍了？
You know, I was thinking, how many
bodies have we dumped in this place?

945
01:21:39,485 --> 01:21:40,861
你知道的，我從不記數
You know, I didn't keep count.

946
01:21:42,155 --> 01:21:44,396
他們都是混蛋，不是麼？
They were all assholes, though, right?

947
01:21:49,203 --> 01:21:50,235
放開她，亞歷克斯
Let her go, Alex.

948
01:21:51,831 --> 01:21:54,998
丹尼打電話說你去拜訪過他
Danny called.
He told me about your visit.

949
01:21:56,502 --> 01:21:59,622
我不得不承認，我都沒想到這一手
I have to admit,
even I didn't see that one coming.

950
01:22:00,465 --> 01:22:03,501
你現在有了錢和碟片
You had the disc and the money.

951
01:22:03,676 --> 01:22:06,084
什麼...
What...

952
01:22:06,262 --> 01:22:09,014
她對你來說意味著什麼？
What is she to you?

953
01:22:11,642 --> 01:22:12,638
生命
Life.

954
01:22:14,562 --> 01:22:17,978
好吧，趁還有命就好好享受吧
Well, enjoy it while it lasts,

955
01:22:18,149 --> 01:22:20,818
不久她就會讓你的小命玩完的
'cause she's the reason
yours is gonna be a whole lot shorter.

956
01:22:21,903 --> 01:22:23,895
錢在哪，路克
The money, Luke.

957
01:22:25,114 --> 01:22:27,107
在車裡
In the car.

958
01:22:30,036 --> 01:22:31,530
或者銀行裡
Or in the bank.

959
01:22:34,582 --> 01:22:37,155
或者在中央車站儲物櫃裡
Or in a series of lockers
at Grand Central.

960
01:22:37,335 --> 01:22:41,463
或者我可能出於好心悉數捐出了
Or maybe I donated it to charity,
out of the goodness of my heart.

961
01:22:43,549 --> 01:22:46,634
想要知道下落，你就得來硬的
You wanna find out where that money is,
you're gonna have to do it the hard way.

962
01:23:43,568 --> 01:23:45,975
你還好吧，梅？
You all right, Mei?

963
01:23:46,154 --> 01:23:49,605
我見過他打斗，你打不過他的
I saw him fight before.
Bad business for you.

964
01:23:50,366 --> 01:23:52,573
是啊，最糟的是
Yeah. The worst.

965
01:23:54,787 --> 01:23:57,574
你又救了我
You saved me, again.

966
01:23:59,000 --> 01:24:00,577
我們救了對方
We save each other.

967
01:24:05,423 --> 01:24:07,131
我知道你在想什麼
I know how you feel.

968
01:24:08,301 --> 01:24:10,543
幫我把這垃圾弄出來
Help me get this sack of garbage
out of the car.

969
01:24:12,930 --> 01:24:15,256
確保他安全回到他老爸那兒
Make sure he gets to his daddy
safe and sound.

970
01:24:18,686 --> 01:24:21,936
5萬，賠償你的損失
50 grand, for your trouble.

971
01:24:22,106 --> 01:24:24,977
錢可能不多，但至少你有命花
Might not seem like much, but at least
you're gonna live to enjoy it.

972
01:24:25,151 --> 01:24:28,899
在經歷了這麼多後，你還想放過他？
You want him safe and sound
after what he did to you?

973
01:24:31,282 --> 01:24:33,109
為了她
For her sake.

